flowchart LR
    A[Growing Game Collection] --> B[Core Problem]

    B --> C[Hard to know what I own]
    B --> D[Hard to keep games organized]
    B --> E[Hard to remember what we played]
    B --> F[Hard to choose what to play next]

    C --> G[Collection Database]
    D --> H[Shelves + Tags]
    E --> I[Play Logging]
    F --> J[Find a Game Filters]

    G --> K[Useful Collection]
    H --> K
    I --> K
    J --> K

    K --> L[Insights]
    L --> M[Unplayed Games]
    L --> N[Player Preferences]
    L --> O[Games to Revisit]
    L --> P[Sell / Trade Candidates]

    M --> Q[Better Decisions]
    N --> Q
    O --> Q
    P --> Q

    Q --> R[The right game for the right group]